title: WATCH: Salomon Rondon wrestling move goes viral
text:
Tweet 
Sunderland's DeAndre Yedlin attempted to head the ball over the Venezuelan international, but soon realised he was in a bit of trouble when struggling to challenge Rondon's 6ft 3in frame. 
Yedlin was primed for a very nasty fall back to earth, but instead Rondon sensationally catches the 10 stone American in his hands,spins him around and puts the defender back on his feet. What do you think?
